verse.name: v1
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Worthy, You are worthy King of kings and Lord of lords You are worthy. Worthy, You are worthy King of kings and Lord of lords I worship You.{/lang-eng}

verse.name: v2
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Holy, You are holy King of kings and Lord of lords You are holy. Holy, You are holy King of kings and Lord of Lords I worship You.{/lang-eng}

verse.name: v3
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Jesus, You are Jesus King of kings and Lord of lords You are Jesus. Jesus, You are Jesus. King of kings and Lord of Lords I worship You.{/lang-eng}
